{
  "stem": "23626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And you know, I didn't even go down-- there was a, there was a road going down the hill where people were supposedly going.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I turn on my back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I slid down that, that steep hill to go as fast down to warn them that he's watching.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Because he would have started shooting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "If I wouldn't have slid down that hill, there would be shooting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know, I could go on and on telling you stories like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But [SIGHS] they so gruesome.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Especially when I keep thinking about those dogs, how many time I saw the flesh of the body on the road and him standing with a big smile and bending his head to the side-- this was the way he would feel very content [BACKROUND NOISE] with himself.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, [BACKROUND NOISE] it wasn't very easy to keep telling you that everything that happened, I really believe that God was with me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Because at that point, where he came looking for me to kill me with his gun in his hand, and I wasn't physically there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Because prior to it, he came down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he said, Susanna, Hana, you have to get out of the villa.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Because there are rumors are going that Jews live in my house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And that's wrong.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So you have to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we moved to the next building, a small house that was occupied by SS women, most horrible women.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were dreadful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were beating people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were treacherous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember their names?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had nothing to do with those people, because I lived only in a villa.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
